        "TileImage": "$($repository 42c0fda2-bb5b-4bbc-963f-821c59fa65b6).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47, your destination is Dartmoor. As the ICA has fallen dangerously short on it&apos;s quota for fish eliminations, we requires your skillset. Your targets are Garret Stevenson, who stole an ICA fish, Jesse Al Binson, who said that Xenoblade 2 was good, Rikki Badcock, who&apos;s cock is so small, putrid, and unwashed (with cheese) she needs to be taken out. Finnaly Badcock&apos;s boyfriend Amos Simpkin, who after sleeping with Rikki, needs to be put out of his misery. I will leave you to prepare.",
